message:
Welcome to Rewards v1.1.5!

In this update, we have patched some app-breaking changes introduced by microsoft.
The support for daily sets in the app will be rolled out soon.

Special Announcement:
You can now earn on upto 15 accounts from one single android device! Click on "Increase your quota" to purchase additional usage quota for cheap, and earn on multiple accounts.

Hope you are enjoying the app experience.
